{"tid":2241531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五眼聯盟要求科技公司為加密應用程式安裝「後門」","createTime":"2020-10-13T11:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T12:56:39.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf12880cdd53243aa8c5e1d00fccd1776d08cce","tid":2241531,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"五眼聯盟國家及印度和日本發表聲明，以公共安全為由，要求科技公司為加密應用程式安裝「後門」，讓執法部門可以取得資料，協助調查犯罪活動。<br />\n<br />\n現時大多數的通訊應用程式，例如Telegram、WhatsApp等，會對資料進行端對端加密，即是只有用家才可讀取或聽取。<br />\n<br />\n由美國、加拿大、英國、澳洲和新西蘭組成的五眼聯盟，聯同印度及日本發表聲明，指有關技術發展迅速，令執法部門調查網上罪案困難重重，對公共安全構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n聲明中以Facebook Messenger為例，指程式在2018年，向美國援助兒童機構提交近1200萬份有關性侵犯兒童的報告；若程式預設使用端對端加密技術，有關報告可能就不能成事。<br />\n<br />\n七國促請科技公司在加密應用程式中加設「後門」，令執法當局可以在合法授權下，取得通訊內容，並在程式設計上加入公共安全考量，容許公司對違法行為採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n聲明亦提到，七國明白加密技術在保護私隱及網絡安全等方面，扮演著重要角色，但不應該完全排除執法。<br />\n<br />\n有維權人士就擔心，如果允許執法部門取得用戶的通訊內容，或會危害民運人士，擴大獨裁政府權力。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，聯盟其中一國澳洲已經有相關法律，要求程式供應商在偵查案件必須時，協助破解加密系統。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=408712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408712&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=d77204d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408712&h=2e856fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=408712</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/article/3105087/five-eyes-india-and-japan-demand-ways-access-whatsapp-other-encrypted\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Farticle%2F3105087%2Ffive-eyes-india-and-japan-demand-ways-access-whatsapp-other-encrypted&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=b2c4516f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/article/3105087/five-eyes-india-and-japan-demand-ways-access-whatsapp-other-encrypted</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/international-statement-end-end-encryption-and-public-safety\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Finternational-statement-end-end-encryption-and-public-safety&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=4ccc7200\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/international-statement-end-end-encryption-and-public-safety</a>"},{"pid":"db38ccde466c87f32c6abaab93cd4576805382c0","tid":2241531,"uid":168366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"Apple一定出聲屌<br />\n但就對住中共隻狗咁"},{"pid":"65baf04f7ae9c73b39c76ae57ce44334d2398911","tid":2241531,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"46a5677930e52c51cbde79a2002e90e97b74fb56","tid":2241531,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a03839d26f64d4393ce70e8ee12eb7c22eb94e9d","tid":2241531,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"51293979c088da6064945c5b2116e571afe545f6","tid":2241531,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"到最後中共一定通過五眼聯盟獲得後門程式"},{"pid":"c6fdabf49f3da4788f9b4925128c1f9ff8ce9de7","tid":2241531,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"而家變做七眼呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5968e84b053152aec3802e5becf7958cfa3099c9","tid":2241531,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51293979c088da6064945c5b2116e571afe545f6","tid":2241531,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"到最後中共一定通過五眼聯盟獲得後門程式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />